      "text": "うん、昨日三枝さんに聞いたんだけど、凄くいい話だ",
      "startTime": 111.3666556278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "大手の製菓メーカーだから大々的に地上波で\n麻奈の姿が流れるんだ。知名度アップ間違いなしだよ",
      "startTime": 119.5666556278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあさ、私の歌も流れるのかな？",
      "startTime": 124.3666556278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん。やってみないか？",
      "startTime": 127.9666556278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_start-04.m4a",
      "text": "やる！　絶対にやるよ！　やらない理由がないよ！！",
      "startTime": 130.8999889611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そう言うと思って、企画書を預かってきた\nさっそく目を通してみてくれ",
      "startTime": 138.9999716678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
